\c 13
\s Abhija mambo waJudha
\p
\v 1 Zvino mugore regumi nemasere ramambo Jerobhoamu, Abhija wakava mambo pamusoro paJudha\x + 1 Madz. 15.1,2.\x*.
\v 2 Wakatonga makore matatu paJerusarema. Uye zita ramai vake raiva Mikaya, mukunda waUrieri\x + 11.20. 1 Madz. 15.2.\x* weGibhiya\x + Josh. 18.28.\x*. Zvino kwakava nehondo pakati paAbhija naJerobhoamu\x + 1 Madz. 15.7.\x*.
\v 3 Zvino Abhija wakasunga hondo ane varwi vevarume veumhare vehondo, varume vakasarudzwa zvuru mazana mana. Jerobhohamu ndokurongedza hondo kurwisana naye ane varume vakasarudzwa zvuru mazana masere, varume veumhare vane simba\x + 14.10. Vato. 20.22. 1 Sam. 17.2.\x*.
\p
\v 4 Zvino Abhija wakamira pamusoro pegomo Zemaraimi\x + 13.19. Josh. 18.22.\x*, riri pagomo raEfuremu\x + Josh. 24.33.\x*, ndokuti: Ndinzwei, Jerobhoamu, naIsraeri wese!
\v 5 Hazvisi zvenyu here kuziva kuti Jehovha Mwari waIsraeri wakapa Dhavhidhi ushe pamusoro paIsraeri nekusingaperi\x + 2 Sam. 7.12,13,16.\x*, kwaari nekuvanakomana vake \add ne\add*sungano yemunyu\x + Num.. 18.19.\x*?
\v 6 Zvakadaro Jerobhoamu mwanakomana waNebhati, muranda waSoromoni mwanakomana waDhavhidhi, wakasimuka ndokumukira ishe wake\x + 1 Madz. 11.26. 12.19,20.\x*.
\v 7 Zvino vakaunganira kwaari varume vasina maturo\x + Vato. 9.4.\x*, vana vaBheriyari\x + Det. 13.13.\x*, vakazvisimbisa kurwisa Rehobhoamu mwanakomana waSoromoni, Rehobhoamu ari mudiki uye akapfava pamoyo asingagoni kuvarwisa\x + 12.13. 2 Madz. 2.23.\x*.
\v 8 Zvino ikozvino munoti muchamirisana neushe hwaJehovha muruoko rwevanakomana vaDhavhidhi\x + 1 Makor. 29.23.\x*; uye imwi muri chaunga chikuru, asi mune mhuru dzegoridhe\x + 1 Madz. 12.28.\x* Jerobhoamu dzaakakuitirai dzive vamwari.
\v 9 Hamuna kudzinga here vapristi vaJehovha, vanakomana vaAroni, neVaRevhi, mukazviitira vapristi semarudzi edzinyika\x + 11.14,15. 1 Madz. 12.31.\x*? Ani nani anouya kuzadza ruoko rwake nenzombe, mhuru yemombe, nemakondohwe manomwe\x + Eki. 29.1.\x*, anova mupristi wevasiri vamwari\x + Jer. 5.7. Det. 32.21.\x*.
\v 10 Asi isu, Jehovha ndiMwari wedu, uye hatina kumusiya; nevapristi vanoshumira Jehovha vari vanakomana vaAroni, neVaRevhi vari pabasa\x + 1 Madz. 15.3.\x*.
\v 11 Zvino vakapisira Jehovha mangwanani nemangwanani uye madekwani nemadekwani zvipo zvinopiswa\x + 2.4.\x*, nezvipfungaidzo zvinonhuhwira\x + 2.4.\x*, nechingwa chekuratidza patafura yakachena\x + 2.4.\x*\x + 4.19. 1 Makor. 9.32.\x*, nechigadziko chemwenje chegoridhe nemwenje yacho\x + 4.20.\x* kupisa madekwani nemadekwani\x + Eki. 27.20,21. Rev. 24.2-4.\x*; nokuti tinochengeta faniro yaJehovha Mwari wedu\x + Num.. 1.53.\x*; asi imwi makamusiya.
\v 12 Zvino tarirai, Mwari anesu ari musoro, nevapristi vake vane hwamanda dzinorira kukuridzirai mhere\x + Num.. 10.9.\x*. Vana vaIsraeri, regai kurwa naJehovha Mwari wemadzibaba enyu; nokuti hamungabudiriri\x + Mab. 5.39.\x*.
\p
\v 13 Asi Jerobhoamu wakapoteredza vavandiri kuti vauye neshure kwavo; naizvozvo vakava pamberi paJudha, uye vavandiri vaiva shure kwavo\x + 20.22. Josh. 8.9. Vato. 9.34. 20.29.\x*.
\v 14 Zvino Judha paakacheuka, tarira, hondo yairwisana navo, mberi neshure; zvino vakachema kuna Jehovha; vapristi ndokuridza hwamanda\x + 13.12.\x*.
\v 15 Zvino varume vaJudha vakaridza mhere. Zvino zvakaitika pakuridza mhere kwevarume vekwaJudha, kuti Mwari wakarova Jerobhoamu naIsraeri wose pamberi paAbhija naJudha\x + 14.12.\x*.
\v 16 Vana vaIsraeri ndokutiza pamberi paJudha; Mwari ndokuvapa muruoko rwavo\x + 16.8. Vato. 3.28.\x*.
\v 17 Zvino Abhija nevanhu vake vakarova pakati pavo nekurova kukuru; ndokuwa vakaurawa kwaIsraeri varume vakasarudzwa zvuru mazana mashanu.
\v 18 Saizvozvo vana vaIsraeri vakaderedzwa nenguva iyo; uye vana vaJudha vakakunda, nokuti vakazembera pana Jehovha Mwari wemadzibaba avo\x + 14.11. 16.7,8. Isa. 10.20. 31.1. 1 Makor. 5.20.\x*.
\v 19 Abhija ndokudzingirirana naJerobhoamu, ndokutapa maguta kubva kwaari: Bheteri nemisha yaro\x + 15.8. 17.2. 1 Madz. 12.30.\x*, neJeshana nemisha yaro, neEfironi nemisha yaro\x + Josh. 15.9. 18.23.\x*.
\v 20 Jerobhoamu haana kuzovazve nesimba pamazuva aAbhija\x + 1 Makor. 29.14.\x*; Jehovha ndokumurova\x + 1 Sam. 25.38.\x*, iye ndokufa\x + 1 Madz. 14.20.\x*.
\p
\v 21 Zvino Abhija wakazvisimbisa, ndokuzvitorera vakadzi gumi nevana, ndokubereka vanakomana makumi maviri nevaviri, nevanasikana gumi nevatanhatu\x + 12.13.\x*.
\v 22 Zvino dzimwe dzenyaya dzaAbhija, nenzira dzake, nemashoko ake, zvakanyorwa munyaya yemuporofita Idho\x + 9.29.\x*.